						"key": "rpfeiffer",
						"displayName": "Ralf Pfeiffer",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "{html}<div><p>We are getting a lot of interest from customers on this. Also PS\nis voting it up.</p>\n<p>Blain, Steve can one of you look at this for the next\nmilestone?</p></div>{html}",
					"updateAuthor": {
						"name": "rpfeiffer",
						"key": "rpfeiffer",
						"displayName": "Ralf Pfeiffer",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
