					"body": "{html}<div><p><a href=\"/projects/32238/changesets/INFO\" title=\n\"Changeset [INFO]\">[INFO]</a> Titanium SDK version: 1.6.0 (01/12/11\n09:38 db09d1e) 4.2.1 4GT and 3.1.3 iphone</p></div>{html}",
