						"displayName": "MelloMike",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "{html}<div><p>Hi Thomas, the problem that we're having is when the 'hires' is\nset to true images are half the size of the ImageView. Just loading\na @2x image with hires set to false works just like it did before\nin 1.5 (at least it does for me)</p>\n<p>So to answer your question, No <a href=\n\"/projects/32238/tickets/2805\" title=\"Ticket #2805\">#2805</a>\ndoesn't totally describe our issue.</p></div>{html}",
